(3, 'medium', 'What is the first normal form (1NF)?', 'Eliminate repeating groups', 'Remove all keys', 'Create indexes', 'Add duplicate columns', 'Eliminate repeating groups', '1NF requires atomic values and no repeating groups.'),
(3, 'medium', 'What does 2NF require?', 'No transitive dependency', 'No partial dependency', 'No primary key', 'No foreign key', 'No partial dependency', '2NF removes partial dependency on a composite key.'),
