(3, 'hard', 'What is referential integrity?', 'Foreign key values must match primary key values', 'Rows must be sorted', 'Columns must be unique', 'Tables must have indexes', 'Foreign key values must match primary key values', 'Referential integrity keeps relationships valid.'),
